  requirements_md = E'- 1-2 years of professional Python development experience or strong academic/personal project background\n- Basic understanding of web frameworks such as Django, Flask, or FastAPI\n- Familiarity with relational databases (PostgreSQL, MySQL) and basic SQL knowledge\n- Understanding of RESTful API concepts and JSON data formats\n- Basic knowledge of version control systems, particularly Git\n- Good problem-solving skills and ability to debug code effectively\n- Strong eagerness to learn new technologies and improve technical skills\n- Basic understanding of software development principles and best practices\n- Ability to work collaboratively in a team environment\n- Good communication skills in English (both written and verbal)\n- Basic knowledge of HTML, CSS, and JavaScript is a plus\n- Familiarity with Linux/Unix environments is advantageous\n- Experience with Docker or containerization is a plus\n- Bachelor''s degree in Computer Science, Software Engineering, or related field (or equivalent practical experience)'
